-- Pentair, Tyco’s Flow-Control Business to Merge
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2012-03-28T10:03:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-28/pentair-tyco-s-flow-control-business-to-merge.html
Pentair Inc. (PNR)  and  Tyco International
Ltd. (TYC)  reported a definitive agreement to combine Tyco’s Flow
Control business with Pentair in a tax-free, all-stock merger.  The transaction values Tyco Flow at about $4.9 billion,
including assumed net debt and minority interest.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  